<br>
Ie: Why would someone join a bunch of strangers in a zone with no loot &amp; less XP -vs- hunting in a zone that offered loot they need or more XP.<br>
<br>
The point s/he was trying to make, I think, being that if it's a group of strangers, and the XP in the zone is less, there's no incentive to travelling out there if not allowed to roll on items s/he could sell.<br>
